##  Objective
Implement a complete CI/CD workflow for a Maven-based Java web application to:

- Automatically pull source code from GitHub on commit  
- Build and package with Maven  
- Containerize with Docker  
- Push image to Docker Hub  
- Deploy to Kubernetes (Amazon EKS)  
- Verify deployment via AWS LoadBalancer URL  
